<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-08-1123 </DOCNO><TEXT>An overview of renewable energies and their importance and potential forEurope is presented. In order to prove the benefit of alternative sourcesof energy to the Community a series of demonstration programmes has beeninitiated aimed at bridging the gap between successful research and developmentand exploitation. An information network entitled SESAME, which is ineffect the European Community's data base for R and D and demonstrationand technology projects will be available to the public later in 1987.</TEXT></DOC>